\begin_inset Formula $h\sqrt{n}\bm{Z}_{p}^{T}(\bm{s})\bm{W}(\bm{s})\left[\bm{Y}-\bm{Z}(\bm{s})\bm{\zeta}(\bm{s})-\frac{h^{2}\kappa_{2}}{2\kappa_{0}}\left\{ \nabla_{uu}^{2}\bm{\zeta}(\bm{s})+\nabla_{vv}^{2}\bm{\zeta}(\bm{s})\right\} \right]=O_{p}(1)$
